"detail view or status line renders.\n"
"\n"
"  %title — %book_pct\n"
"  → Dune — 36%\n"
"\n"
"Wrap content in [if:foo]…[/if] to show it only when the token has a value. "
"Add [else]…[/if] for a fallback.\n"
"\n"
"  [if:series]Book %series_num of %series_name[/if]\n"
"  [if:batt<20]LOW %batt[/if]"
